#

Quick Instant Pot Borscht

45 min
$10
200 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

dairy

Dietary Tags:

vegetariangluten-free

Cuisine:

Eastern European

Course:

Soup

Tags:

soupinstant potquick meal

Description

A vibrant and hearty beet soup, rich in flavor and nutrients, perfect for a quick meal.

Ingredients

  • beets: 4 medium, peeled and diced
  • cabbage: 2 cups, shredded
  • carrots: 2 medium, diced
  • potatoes: 2 medium, diced
  • onion: 1 large, chopped
  • vegetable broth: 4 cups
  • apple cider vinegar: 2 tablespoons
  • sour cream: for topping
  • fresh dill: for garnish
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
